  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de Ark</title>

    <!--
    <para>
First, fix a problem identified upstream:</para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../ark-&kf5apps-version;-upstream_fix-1.patch</userinput></screen>
-->
<para>
      Instale <application>Ark</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$KF5_PREFIX \
      -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release         \
      -DBUILD_TESTING=OFF                \
      -Wno-dev .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

